Description: Tools for creating concentration curves to visualize inequality 
    and disproportionate distributions. Concentration curves plot the cumulative 
    proportion of a health outcome or resource against the cumulative proportion 
    of a population ranked by some variable of interest. The package 
    provides a ggplot2 geom for easy integration with existing workflows and 
    functions for data preprocessing and concentration index calculation.
Imports: ggplot2 

